\n總之係果種有得食一定食既貨色。<br />\n佢三年前結婚，果時我仲有去飲，我最記得佢老公，三十出頭已經早生華髮，係做工程的，<br />\n唔夠一年，就離婚了。<br />\n<br />\n我跟咗呢位女上司5年，開頭一兩年我同佢除咗工作基本上冇交流。之後可能合作耐咗，工作上又越來越有默契，我同佢之間既距離開始拉近。<br />\n<br />\n係一次傾計中，佢得知我放假間中會行山同露營，佢即刻表現出強烈既興趣，仲話下次要約埋佢。"},{"pid":"66a827441630613493107cb3b58ba3d8eedeeb19","tid":1756621,"uid":156065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"識野 K dot"},{"pid":"3b81c5849346da647c90897c199b602d201f202b","tid":1756621,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"你唔自爆都唔知問你咩好，不如你開新AC好過啦!"},{"pid":"c2272183eb427cd6692433879b31f93109826903","tid":1756621,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"db8b498ed1295a67c2fd5b0da5cecb2e823a2f2c","tid":1756621,"uid":111372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dfc37f84c3d5b438d7c6048682510e14f27c13a","tid":1756621,"uid":218659,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"收到wind 樓主嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pvXeij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pvXeij.jpg&h=2add1488&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"我都覺得呢個係樓主"},{"pid":"057a45727a6c54c08dcec9c92b81d792c9c6299e","tid":1756621,"uid":234271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15b2c8e7bf3d35e69393a3676a2882552e5687ea","tid":1756621,"uid":251052,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"0c733ce16c59268c144135a89d72b87442ae09db","tid":1756621,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"有咩計劃攪好民生工作？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"興建社區資訊連儂牆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"用咩條例/權力興建、指定<br />\n對於破壞者用咩條例指控<br />\n如何判定破壞者同更新連儂牆人士<br />\n會否定期（例如逢星期三1200-2100）係連儂牆接受質詢"},{"pid":"d8c0fcc3db4a245e3f5ffc3c8cbf28fada1d1971","tid":1756621,"uid":4